  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 250°C and place a pizza stone or baking sheet inside.",
    "Roll out dough on a lightly floured surface to a 25 cm diameter circle.",
    "Brush dough with olive oil and evenly spread tomato sauce across the base.",
    "Sprinkle shio‑koji over the sauce, then layer sliced mozzarella and grated parmesan.",
    "Bake on the preheated stone for 12 minutes until crust is golden and cheese bubbly.",
    "Remove pizza, sprinkle fresh black pepper, then add flaked seaweed and arugula.",
    "Slice into wedges and serve immediately while hot."
